			<div class="container gap-200"></div>
			<div class="container history-stop-02 fade-in-500 trigger-foodchain">
				<h2 class="fade-in-600">The disrupted food chain.</h2>
				<p class="content offset fade-in-700 trigger-surface-light trigger-urchin">
					Sea otters eat urchins. Urchins eat kelp. 
					When the sea otters disappeared, this allowed the urchin population 
					to flourish, and over time they decimated 95% of our local kelp forests.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>		
	
	
	
		
